description: This common Sakura purrs with a rating of 97, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 97, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 1 for North, Stringalong for East, 2 for South, and 3 for West. Sakura has the personality suit of whale. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Sakura [97 Votes, Common]
